// Minimal agent: just a constructor and a default. Desugars to a
// persistent for over `fooCtor` whose body opens `new this, private`,
// runs the (empty) constructor body, sends bundle+{*this} back to
// the reply channel, and listens persistently on `this` for method
// calls -- the match falls through to the (no-op) default arm.
new fooCtor in {
  agent fooCtor {
    constructor() { Nil } |
    default(...@args) { Nil }
  }
}
